<section class="section">
{{> 'partials/breadcrumbs_common' }}
    <h1 class="title is-1">
        Bot: {{bot.Name}}
    </h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
        {{bot.Info}}
    </p>

    <div class="content">
        <p>States and Variables make up this Bots data.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
        <div class="box">
            <h1 class="title is-big">States</h1>
            <div class="content">
            {{#each botGroup.States as |state stateIndex|}} <!-- Action:Start -->
                <p>
                <strong>{{state.Name}}</strong>:
                {{#each state.Labels as |label labelIndex|}} <!-- Action:Start -->
                    <span class="tag {{#if_slice_has_dot_strings_2 bot.StateValues state.Name label }}is-success{{else}}is-info-light{{/if_slice_has_dot_strings_2}} has-tooltip-arrow" data-tooltip="{{#if_slice_has_dot_strings_2 bot.StateValues state.Name label }}This is the Active State: {{state.Name}}.{{label}}{{else}}This state is not active.{{/if_slice_has_dot_strings_2}}" style="border-bottom: 0px solid !important;">{{label}}</span>
                {{/each}}
                </p>
            {{/each}} <!-- Action:End -->
            </div>

            <h1 class="title is-big">Variables</h1>
            {{> 'partials/bot/taglist_variable_value' }}

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Action gets a Final Score, on the left side of the header, and will be green or red depending on whether it
            is Available to executed.</p>
    </div>

    {{#each bot.SortedActionData as |actionData actionDataIndex|}} <!-- Action:Start -->
        {{#with_action_from_bot botGroup bot actionDataIndex as |action|}}
            {{> 'partials/action/card_box' }}
        {{/with_action_from_bot}}
    {{/each}} <!-- Action:End -->

    <div class="content">
        <p></p>
        <p>Actions can only be Available if their Required States are currently active.  There is a description if you
            expand them which explains the scoring in detail, up to the final score.</p>
        <p>An Action with a score of 0 will never be executed, and there are several conditions which will force a 0 score.</p>
        <p>When more than one Action is Available and meets all their requirements, the highest score will be executed.</p>
    </div>
</section>
<script>
    $(function() { HandlePageDataReloads('/api/web/bot', "{{{ input_data }}}", "{{{ interactive_control }}}"); });
</script>
